476
00:26:02.375 --> 00:26:03.708
Shoot!

477
00:26:05.291 --> 00:26:06.791
Shoot!

478
00:26:08.125 --> 00:26:09.416
Zakhele.

479
00:26:10.833 --> 00:26:11.916
